Name: Currency Code
Description: The currency code used in the cart.

Name: HubSpot Team
Description: The primary team of the owner.

Name: Billing City
Description: The city for the billing address.

Name: Billing Country
Description: The country for the billing address.

Name: Billing Phone Number
Description: The phone number for the billing address.

Name: Billing ZIP/Postal Code
Description: The ZIP/postal code for the billing address.

Name: Billing State
Description: The state for the billing address.

Name: Billing Street
Description: The street for the billing address.

Name: Buyer accepts marketing
Description: Whether the customer would like to receive updates (sms/email) from the shop.

Name: Name
Description: Name in an external system for the cart.

Name: Cart Url
Description: The recovery URL that's sent to a customer so they can recover their cart if it is abandoned.

Name: Created by user ID
Description: The user that created this object. This value is automatically set by HubSpot and may not be modified.

Name: Object create date/time
Description: The date and time at which this object was created. This value is automatically set by HubSpot and may not be modified.

Name: Exchange rate
Description: This is the exchange rate used to convert the cart amount into your company currency.

Name: Cart ID
Description: Unique identifier in an external system for the cart.

Name: Created Date
Description: The date/time the abandoned cart was created.

Name: Modified Date
Description: The date/time the cart details were last updated.

Name: Status
Description: Current status of the cart as recorded on the source system.

Name: Token
Description: A unique ID for cart in external system.

Name: Landing Site
Description: The URL of the first page on the sellers site that the customer landed on prior to them placing the order.

Name: Object last modified date/time
Description: Most recent timestamp of any property update for this object. This includes HubSpot internal properties, which can be visible or hidden. This property is updated automatically.

Name: Merged record IDs
Description: The list of record IDs that have been merged into this record. This value is automatically set by HubSpot and may not be modified.

Name: Record ID
Description: The unique ID for this record. This value is automatically set by HubSpot and may not be modified.

Name: Record Source Detail 1
Description: First level of detail on how this record was created

Name: Record Source Detail 2
Description: Second level of detail on how this record was created

Name: Record Source Detail 3
Description: Third level of detail on how this record was created

Name: Record Source
Description: How this record was created

Name: Referring Site
Description: The URL of the site that the customer came from to arrive at the sellers site prior to placing their order.

Name: Shipping City
Description: The city for the shipping address.

Name: Shipping Country
Description: The country for the shipping address.

Name: Shipping Phone Number
Description: The phone number for the shipping address.

Name: Shipping ZIP/Postal Code
Description: The ZIP/postal code for the shipping address.

Name: Shipping State
Description: The state for the shipping address.

Name: Shipping Street
Description: The street for the shipping address.

Name: Source Store
Description: Data used to identify which store the order came from.

Name: Tags
Description: A collection of tag strings associated with the order.

Name: Total Weight
Description: The total weight of the order for shipping purposes.

Name: Updated by user ID
Description: The user that last updated this object. This value is automatically set by HubSpot and may not be modified.

Name: Owner Assigned Date
Description: The most recent date an owner was assigned to this object. This is set automatically by HubSpot and can be used for segmentation and reporting.

Name: Owner
Description: The owner of the object.

Name: Cart Discount
Description: Amount of discount on the cart

Name: Discount Codes
Description: Discount Codes on a cart.

Name: Amount in company currency
Description: The amount of the cart, using the exchange rate, in your company's currency

Name: Shipping Cost
Description: The base cost (i.e. undiscounted), in the orders associated currency, associated with shipping the order.

Name: Subtotal Price
Description: Total order amount before discounts, tax, duties etc.

Name: Tax Price
Description: Tax amount associated with the order, including duties.

Name: Total Price
Description: Sum Total amount associated with this order.
